Visual Controls For LUA (VCLua)

version 0.3.5
platform WIN32, LINUX, MacOS
luaversion 5.1.4
date 18/11/2010
--------------
supports 44 visible controls, 9 dialogs and 5 invisible controls

+ added GetScreenSize function 
+ added ItemAtPos function to listboxes
* Windows theme support added
* Unix support improved
* minor bugfixes

version 0.3.4
platform WIN32, LINUX, MacOS
luaversion 5.1.4
date 29/10/2010
--------------
supports 44 visible controls, 9 dialogs and 5 invisible controls

+ added some anchoring features to visible components 
  ( http://wiki.lazarus.freepascal.org/Anchor_Sides [thx to Michail Svetlov for the link] )
* VCL.xxxxxx, contol creating function now accepts property table 
  [e.g lab01 = VCL.Label{name = "lab01", top = 10, left = 10, caption = "This is a Label"} ]
+ added VCL.FileExists and VCL.DirectoryExist functions
* minor bugfixes

version 0.3.3
platform WIN32, LINUX, MacOS
luaversion 5.1.4
date 10/02/2010
--------------
supports 44 visible controls, 9 dialogs and 5 invisible controls

* html documentation changed
* EditButton buttonclick event bug corrected
* StringGrids bugs corrected

version 0.3.2
platform WIN32, LINUX, MacOS
luaversion 5.1.4
date 26/01/2010
--------------
supports 44 visible controls, 9 dialogs and 5 invisible controls

+ html documentation completed and available at VCLua project homepage
+ FindDlg and ReplaceDlg dialogs added
+ SynEdit highlighters added: c/c++,css,java,pascal,perl,php,sql,tex,xml,html and shellscript
+ SynEdit highlighter now has load/save methods
+ StrinGrid AddRow method added (for insert and add)
* SynEdit text property handling corrected
* SynEdit highlighted text can be saved as html
* [[ ]] handling in Lua highlighter corrected
* FileListBox Filename property corrected
* DateEdit value now can be accessed via 'date' or 'text' property
* fixed icon and image loading from lua table
* fixed menu find, add, insert methods
* parent property bug corrected

