version 0.1.9
platform WIN32
luaversion 5.1 and 5.0
date 11/08/2006
--------------
+ ImageList added
+ Tree has new functions  
	:Images(imagelist)
	:SetImage(nodeindex,imageindex)
	:SetSelectedImage(nodeindex,imageindex)
* Tree :SetItems function corrected, now accepts the text,data,image and selected properties
* Tree setdata/getdata bug corrected (thx to Kaptain N [e-home@ukr.net])
* bugfix in LuaControl module, eventname = nil command now clears the event

